{
  "stem": "13096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I was-- I never dream what was in store to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They tell us that we are going to go to-- to Greece.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you were at the barges, you know, we are told, if, you know-- I suppose, that we knew that what it was in store for us, maybe we would have tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If we knew it was, you know, it was going to be the end of us, anybody, even the young people, they could have escaped or tried to do something-- even, you know, to put yourself in danger.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So better, you know, to be killed to go all through all this-- all this horror.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we never knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We never expected.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never saw any violence before in Rhodes Island.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I said, the Italians were very gentle people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Germans who came to, you know, to stay in the island during the war, they were always Wehrmacht-- Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, they were not SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They start-- we start, you know, witnessing violence when we arrive, you know, in Athens, in Piraeus.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- you know, the-- from Rhodes to Athens is a small distance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, on a clear day, you know, even Turkey, it is a very short distance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On a clear days, from Rhodes Island, you know, beach, you can see, you know, on a clear day, you can see some mountains of the Turkey and some even far away-- so-- distances.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so, actually, usually, you know, they take like, a-- like one day or two days to reach Rhodes Island to-- as this was short-- a short distance-- to-- to Greece.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that journey lasted eight days-- eight days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the fact, you know, that during the day, we were stationary.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
